glslScene is also licensed under the zlib license.
If you have lawyers who are unhappy with public domain. Every source file (excepted external libraries)
includes an explicit dual-license for you to choose from.

glslScene scene projects (scenes subdirectory):
If no own license exists in the directory of the specific scene project or
no other license information exists, then the corresponding scene project is also
under the public domain or zlib license (dual licensed).

